channel.title: Editable Silab Client Version?
channel.description: Hello. I was wondering if there's a silabsoft client that is editable and open. I need this for one reason only. Most of the items in my server that I and my other players have are only in the silab client. If I download another client and use it, all it does is show up as null. I mean there are hundreds and hundreds of items that are nulled so I can't just add them all..... Is there a client?
